Croogo Facebook Blog Plugin
------------------------------
Plugin will download your Facebook Page RSS feed and add them as
published (optional) blog node posts


How to use
------------------------------
- Log in to admin panel
- Go to Extensions > Plugins page
- Upload the zip file (available here)
- Click on tick/cross icon of 'FacebookBlog' for activating or deactivating the plugin


Notes
------------------------------
- Various settings
- Tries to generate a decent title and slug but not 100%
- Only works for Croogo 1.2 at the moment

